item.description:
Enjoy a relaxing evening listening to the music of Trisha and Phil Knudsen
They are hosts of the Monday acoustic open Mike at The Center for Arts in Natick. They have opened for Bill Staines and Don White, as well as appearing on NECN TV station's morning coffeehouse series. Phil is a guitarist and songwriter and trisha is a talented Poet.

Meet in the function room located in the back of the store. Come early to browse the gift shop - they have lots of great stuff. There is also a cafe so grab a beverage and bring it to the performance.

Concert is from 6:30 to 8:30 pm.

Hope to see you there!
item.name: Free Concert at Tatnuck
